Represented Australia in MWC 7K 2014/2016
Started at O2JAM when I was 8yrs old.
I hate 200+bpm chord streaming, I love chords.
Keyboard: Ducky Zero Mechanical Keyboard Cherry Red with double O'rings (1.5mm thick each) for SDF (space) JKL
I used to be a laptop keyboard skrub...
EDM is life, Overwatch took my motivation to play osu!mania...
I stream usually weekends or something
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/apocazumbee
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/zumbee-3
